text: Atlético Porcuna Club de Fútbol is a Spanish football team based in Porcuna, Jaén, in the autonomous community of Andalusia. Founded in 1975 it currently plays in Tercera División – Group 9, holding home matches at Estadio Municipal San Benito, with a capacity of 1,200 spectators. == History == The club was founded in 1975
